title: Disney Who's Who
description: Who's who! Get to know more about your favorite characters - and meet some you may not know - in this comprehensive guide!What is the name of Alice's cat? Who is Gilbert Huph? How many hairs does Elsa have on her head? Don't know? You soon will!With more than 600 characters bios and a whole host of fun facts, you'll be a Disney expert in no time!
author: Walt Disney Company
